{"tid":164674,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[PKM吹雞!!!]MSS冬季賽事","createTime":"2017-03-21T00:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T03:47:11.000Z","uid":41342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8156b50b55e956b1045d4269f33fa635cb1e99e6","tid":164674,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【官方賽事】【2016-2017 Midseason Showdown 季中賽事 (Winter Series 冬季系列) 】</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港Pokemon官方電玩賽季中賽事 (冬季系列)(Midseason Showdown, Winter Series)！<br />\n累計成績優異的玩家，更有機會代表香港出戰2017年8月份的2017年寵物小精靈世界錦標賽！<br />\n在新設的計分賽制下，超級挑戰賽(Premier Challenge)將會分成3個季度，而每個季度均會計算玩家最高分的2場比賽！就算錯失了1場，只要在之後的比賽補回錯失的場數，就可以取得取回分數的機會！對比起地區賽 ( Regional Championship )，季中大戰 ( Midseason Showdowns )的規模相對較少。季中大戰 ( Midseason Showdowns )給予玩家機會去取得更多的冠軍點數 ( Championship Points )，而且也是個機會去測驗自己的實力和為大型比賽進行準備。本賽事歡迎所有玩家參與。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：2017 年 3 月 25 日 (星期六)<br />\n地點：新蒲崗太子道東638號 Mikiki商場 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報名時間：10:00am-11:00noon (官方賽事，逾時不候)<br />\n參賽登記費：$50</span><br />\n參賽人數上限：100人<br />\n<br />\n比賽當天報到前，必須<span style=\"font-size: large;\">自行列印及填寫下表</span>，申報所有出戰精靈資料(中/英/日), 方可參賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(貼唔到doc.  所以自己睇link)<br />\n<a href=\"http://playpokemonhk.com/2017/03/12/mss_winter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaypokemonhk.com%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2Fmss_winter%2F&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1a02ae1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://playpokemonhk.com/2017/03/12/mss_winter/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持本地PKM賽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772195fdd69974648c7c3a6c8d63e4adb0d9d85b","tid":164674,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"聞說個搞手dum左成皮幾野去搞個比賽<br />\n有時間有地點就係唔多人!!!<br />\n<br />\n(P.S. 如果想入PKM wtsapp group就PM我  入面乜人都有 就係無女)<br />\n<br />\n(利申：玩緊MH，到時我會到場為入唔到top cut既人一齊升HR<br />\n(利利申：得HR12...打闇螳吹笛可sup)"},{"pid":"1a081776392dd7ea8eb196da05c9e41e85b4926a","tid":164674,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"6680eb23151ec04ffa52a0199a1181bf3698c521","tid":164674,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n多啲人參加係好事<br />\nPlayers又多啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e82cda32ebe130ba7f18af2547ec648cf94653","tid":164674,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聞說個搞手dum左成皮幾野去搞個比賽<br />\n有時間有地點就係唔多人!!!<br />\n<br />\n(P.S. 如果想入PKM wtsapp group就PM我  入面乜人都有 就係無女)<br />\n<br />\n(利申：玩緊MH，到時我會到場為入唔到top cut既人一齊升HR<br />\n(利利申：得HR12...打闇螳吹笛可sup)</blockquote><br />\n你地圍內whatsapp group有冇高手？"},{"pid":"2ff392ae0c7a0dbc69d502e4604a7db2ba074108","tid":164674,"uid":72631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9900f5c1abee415e81d13b9e845b3750c16e9afb","tid":164674,"uid":59885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e52ba7cbb9e6f6bc9a43f69ef9de9a29764fbae4","tid":164674,"uid":4549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"又話反寶可夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid